INSERT INTO `tb_assunto` VALUES (1,'Grandezas proporcionais','Saiba um pouco mais sobre grandezas proporcionais. ','<p>Definimos por grandeza tudo aquilo que pode ser contado e medido, como o tempo, a velocidade, comprimento, pre&ccedil;o, idade, temperatura entre outros. As grandezas s&atilde;o classificadas em: diretamente proporcionais e inversamente proporcionais.<br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><em style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Grandezas diretamente proporcionais<br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /></strong></em><br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />S&atilde;o aquelas grandezas onde a varia&ccedil;&atilde;o de uma provoca a varia&ccedil;&atilde;o da outra numa mesma raz&atilde;o. Se uma dobra a outra dobra, se uma triplica a outra triplica, se uma &eacute; divida em duas partes iguais a outra tamb&eacute;m &eacute; divida &agrave; metade.<br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><em style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Exemplo 1<br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /></strong></em><br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />Se tr&ecirc;s cadernos custam R$ 8,00, o pre&ccedil;o de seis cadernos custar&aacute; R$ 16,00. Observe que se dobramos o n&uacute;mero de cadernos tamb&eacute;m dobramos o valor dos cadernos. Confira pela tabela:<br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><img style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://s1.static.brasilescola.uol.com.br/be/e/Untitled-13(30).jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"259\" height=\"125\" /></p>\r\n<p><br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><em style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Exemplo 2<br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /></strong></em><br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />Para percorrer 300 km, um carro gastou 30 litros de combust&iacute;vel. Nas mesmas condi&ccedil;&otilde;es, quantos quil&ocirc;metros o carro percorrer&aacute; com 60 litros? E com 120 litros?<br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><img style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://s1.static.brasilescola.uol.com.br/be/e/Untitled-2(99).jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"210\" height=\"132\" /></p>\r\n<p><br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><em style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Grandezas inversamente proporcionais<br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /></strong></em><br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />Uma grandeza &eacute; inversamente proporcional quando opera&ccedil;&otilde;es inversas s&atilde;o utilizadas nas grandezas. Por exemplo, se dobramos uma das grandezas temos que dividir a outra por dois, se triplicamos uma delas devemos dividir a outra por tr&ecirc;s e assim sucessivamente. A velocidade e o tempo s&atilde;o considerados grandezas inversas, pois aumentarmos a velocidade, o tempo &eacute; reduzido, e se diminu&iacute;mos a velocidade, o tempo aumenta.<br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><em style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Exemplo 3</strong></em><br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />Para encher um tanque s&atilde;o necess&aacute;rias 30 vasilhas de 6 litros cada uma. Se forem usadas vasilhas de 3 litros cada, quantas ser&atilde;o necess&aacute;rias?<br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><br style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><img style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://s1.static.brasilescola.uol.com.br/be/e/Untitled-3(85).jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"213\" height=\"109\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Utilizaremos 60 vasilhas, pois se a capacidade da vasilha diminui, o n&uacute;mero de vasilhas aumenta no intuito de encher o tanque.<br style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><br style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><br style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />As duas grandezas s&atilde;o muito utilizadas em situa&ccedil;&otilde;es de compara&ccedil;&atilde;o, isto &eacute; comum no cotidiano. A utiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o da regra de tr&ecirc;s nos casos envolvendo proporcionalidade direta e inversa &eacute; de extrema import&acirc;ncia para a obten&ccedil;&atilde;o dos resultados.</p>\r\n<p style=\"background: 0px 0px #ffffff; font-family: Raleway; font-size: 20px; margin: 0px 0px 15px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"background: 0px 0px #ffffff; font-family: Raleway; font-size: 20px; margin: 0px 0px 15px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" align=\"justify\">C&acute;reditos:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"background: 0px 0px #ffffff; font-family: Raleway; font-size: 20px; margin: 0px 0px 15px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" align=\"justify\"><a href=\"https://brasilescola.uol.com.br/matematica/proporcionalidade-entre-grandezas.htm\">https://brasilescola.uol.com.br/matematica/proporcionalidade-entre-grandezas.htm</a></p>','1.png',1,1,1),(2,'Regra de três simples','Regra de três simples. Estude sobre este assunto para efetuar a prova do Enem. ','<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Regra de tr&ecirc;s simples &eacute; um processo pr&aacute;tico para resolver problemas que envolvam quatro valores dos quais conhecemos tr&ecirc;s deles. Devemos, portanto, determinar um valor a partir dos tr&ecirc;s j&aacute; conhecidos.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 1.3em; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 1.3em; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Passos utilizados numa regra de tr&ecirc;s simples</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">1&ordm;)</span>&nbsp;Construir uma tabela, agrupando as grandezas da mesma esp&eacute;cie em colunas e mantendo na mesma linha as grandezas de esp&eacute;cies diferentes em correspond&ecirc;ncia.</p>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">2&ordm;)</span>&nbsp;Identificar se as grandezas s&atilde;o diretamente ou inversamente proporcionais.</p>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">3&ordm;)</span>&nbsp;Montar a propor&ccedil;&atilde;o e resolver a equa&ccedil;&atilde;o.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 1.3em; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Exemplos</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span class=\"azul\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000ff;\">1)</span>&nbsp;Com uma &aacute;rea&nbsp; de absor&ccedil;&atilde;o de raios solares de 1,2m<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\">2</span>, uma lancha com motor movido a energia solar consegue produzir 400 watts por hora de energia. Aumentando-se essa &aacute;rea para 1,5m<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\">2</span>, qual ser&aacute; a energia produzida?</p>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Solu&ccedil;&atilde;o:</em>&nbsp;montando a tabela:</p>\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table style=\"border-spacing: 0px;\" border=\"0\" width=\"48%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"5\">\r\n<tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#CCCCCC\" width=\"50%\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">&Aacute;rea (m<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\">2</span>)</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#CCCCCC\" width=\"50%\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">Energia (Wh)</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#EEEEEE\" width=\"50%\">1,2</td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#EEEEEE\" width=\"50%\">400</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#EEEEEE\" width=\"50%\">1,5</td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#EEEEEE\" width=\"50%\">x</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Identifica&ccedil;&atilde;o do tipo de rela&ccedil;&atilde;o:</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.somatematica.com.br/fundam/regra3_1.gif\" width=\"91\" height=\"52\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Inicialmente colocamos uma seta para baixo na coluna que cont&eacute;m o x (2&ordf; coluna). Observe que,&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">aumentando</span>&nbsp;a &aacute;rea de absor&ccedil;&atilde;o, a energia solar&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">aumenta</span>. Como as palavras correspondem (aumentando - aumenta), podemos afirmar que as grandezas s&atilde;o&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">diretamente proporcionais</span>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Assim sendo, colocamos uma outra seta no mesmo sentido (para baixo) na 1&ordf; coluna.&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Montando a propor&ccedil;&atilde;o e resolvendo a equa&ccedil;&atilde;o temos</em>:</p>\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table style=\"border-spacing: 0px;\" border=\"0\" width=\"62%\" cellspacing=\"3\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" width=\"50%\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.somatematica.com.br/fundam/regra3_2.gif\" width=\"97\" height=\"54\" /></td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" width=\"50%\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.somatematica.com.br/fundam/regra3_3.gif\" width=\"114\" height=\"112\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Logo, a energia produzida ser&aacute; de&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">500 watts por hora</span>.</p>\r\n<hr style=\"box-sizing: content-box; height: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; border-top: 0px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-right-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-bottom-style: dashed; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\" />\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span class=\"azul\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000ff;\">2)</span>&nbsp;Um trem, deslocando-se a uma velocidade m&eacute;dia de 400Km/h, faz um determinado percurso em 3 horas. Em quanto tempo faria esse mesmo percurso, se a velocidade utilizada fosse de 480km/h?</p>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Solu&ccedil;&atilde;o:</em>&nbsp;montando a tabela:</p>\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table style=\"border-spacing: 0px;\" border=\"0\" width=\"48%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"5\">\r\n<tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#CCCCCC\" width=\"50%\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">Velocidade (Km/h)</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#CCCCCC\" width=\"50%\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">Tempo (h)</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#EEEEEE\" width=\"50%\">400</td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#EEEEEE\" width=\"50%\">3</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#EEEEEE\" width=\"50%\">480</td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#EEEEEE\" width=\"50%\">x</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Identifica&ccedil;&atilde;o do tipo de rela&ccedil;&atilde;o:</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.somatematica.com.br/fundam/regra3_4.gif\" width=\"121\" height=\"50\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Inicialmente colocamos uma seta para baixo na coluna que cont&eacute;m o x (2&ordf; coluna). Observe que,&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">aumentando</span>&nbsp;a velocidade, o tempo do percurso&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">diminui</span>. Como as palavras s&atilde;o contr&aacute;rias (aumentando - diminui), podemos afirmar que as grandezas s&atilde;o&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">inversamente proporcionais</span>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Assim, colocamos uma outra seta no sentido contr&aacute;rio (para cima) na 1&ordf; coluna.&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Montando a propor&ccedil;&atilde;o e resolvendo a equa&ccedil;&atilde;o temos</em>:</p>\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table style=\"border-spacing: 0px;\" border=\"0\" width=\"62%\" cellspacing=\"3\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" width=\"50%\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.somatematica.com.br/fundam/regra3_5.gif\" width=\"124\" height=\"47\" /></td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" width=\"50%\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.somatematica.com.br/fundam/regra3_6.gif\" width=\"162\" height=\"131\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Logo, o tempo desse percurso seria de&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">2,5 horas ou 2 horas e 30 minutos</span>.</p>\r\n<hr style=\"box-sizing: content-box; height: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; border-top: 0px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-right-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-bottom-style: dashed; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\" />\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span class=\"azul\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000ff;\">3)</span>&nbsp;Bianca comprou 3 camisetas e pagou R$120,00. Quanto ela pagaria se comprasse 5 camisetas do mesmo tipo e pre&ccedil;o?</p>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Solu&ccedil;&atilde;o:</em>&nbsp;montando a tabela:</p>\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table style=\"border-spacing: 0px;\" border=\"0\" width=\"40%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"5\">\r\n<tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#CCCCCC\" width=\"50%\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">Camisetas</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#CCCCCC\" width=\"50%\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">Pre&ccedil;o (R$)</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#EEEEEE\" width=\"50%\">3</td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#EEEEEE\" width=\"50%\">120</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#EEEEEE\" width=\"50%\">5</td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#EEEEEE\" width=\"50%\">x</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Observe que,&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">aumentando</span>&nbsp;o n&uacute;mero de camisetas, o pre&ccedil;o&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">aumenta</span>. Como as palavras correspondem (aumentando - aumenta), podemos afirmar que as grandezas s&atilde;o&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">diretamente proporcionais</span>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Montando a propor&ccedil;&atilde;o e resolvendo a equa&ccedil;&atilde;o temos</em>:</p>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.somatematica.com.br/fundam/regra3_7.gif\" width=\"107\" height=\"107\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Logo, a Bianca pagaria&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">R$200,00</span>&nbsp;pelas 5 camisetas.</p>\r\n<hr style=\"box-sizing: content-box; height: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; border-top: 0px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-right-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-bottom-style: dashed; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\" />\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span class=\"azul\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000ff;\">4)</span>&nbsp;Uma equipe de oper&aacute;rios, trabalhando 8 horas por dia, realizou determinada obra em 20 dias. Se o n&uacute;mero de horas de servi&ccedil;o for reduzido para 5 horas por dia, em que prazo essa equipe far&aacute; o mesmo trabalho?</p>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Solu&ccedil;&atilde;o:</em>&nbsp;montando a tabela:</p>\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table style=\"border-spacing: 0px;\" border=\"0\" width=\"51%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"5\">\r\n<tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#CCCCCC\" width=\"38%\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">Horas por dia</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#CCCCCC\" width=\"62%\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">Prazo para t&eacute;rmino (dias)</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#EEEEEE\" width=\"38%\">8</td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#EEEEEE\" width=\"62%\">20</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#EEEEEE\" width=\"38%\">5</td>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#EEEEEE\" width=\"62%\">x</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Observe que,&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">diminuindo</span>&nbsp;o n&uacute;mero de horas trabalhadas por dia, o prazo para t&eacute;rmino&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">aumenta</span>. Como as palavras s&atilde;o contr&aacute;rias (diminuindo - aumenta), podemos afirmar que as grandezas s&atilde;o&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">inversamente proporcionais</span>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Montando a propor&ccedil;&atilde;o e resolvendo a equa&ccedil;&atilde;o temos</em>:</p>\r\n<p class=\"justificado\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.somatematica.com.br/fundam/regra3_8.gif\" width=\"151\" height=\"131\" /></p>','2.png',1,1,2),(3,'Estatística, gráficos e tabelas','Estatística, gráficos e tabelas. Confira os 3 assuntos importantes. ','<p>Os&nbsp;<strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">gr&aacute;ficos</strong>&nbsp;s&atilde;o representa&ccedil;&otilde;es que facilitam a an&aacute;lise de dados, os quais costumam ser dispostos em tabelas quando se realiza pesquisas&nbsp;<a style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" href=\"https://brasilescola.uol.com.br/matematica/estatistica-1.htm\">estat&iacute;sticas</a>. Eles&nbsp;<strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">trazem muito mais praticidade</strong>, principalmente quando os dados n&atilde;o s&atilde;o discretos, ou seja, quando s&atilde;o n&uacute;meros consideravelmente grandes. Al&eacute;m disso, os gr&aacute;ficos tamb&eacute;m apresentam de maneira evidente os dados em seu aspecto temporal.</p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Leia tamb&eacute;m</strong>:&nbsp;<a style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" href=\"https://brasilescola.uol.com.br/matematica/o-que-margem-erro-uma-pesquisa.htm\">O que &eacute; a margem de erro em uma pesquisa?</a></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"background: 0px 0px #ffffff; font-family: Raleway; font-size: 22px; margin: 40px 0px 20px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; top: 0px; left: 0px; cursor: text; font-weight: 500; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Elementos do gr&aacute;fico</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Ao construirmos um gr&aacute;fico em estat&iacute;stica, devemos levar em considera&ccedil;&atilde;o alguns elementos que s&atilde;o essenciais para sua melhor compreens&atilde;o.&nbsp;<strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Um gr&aacute;fico deve ser simples</strong>&nbsp;devido &agrave; necessidade de passar uma informa&ccedil;&atilde;o de maneira mais r&aacute;pida e coesa, ou seja, em um gr&aacute;fico estat&iacute;stico, n&atilde;o deve haver muitas informa&ccedil;&otilde;es, devemos colocar nele somente o necess&aacute;rio.</p>\r\n<p>As informa&ccedil;&otilde;es em um gr&aacute;fico devem estar dispostas de maneira&nbsp;<strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">clara</strong>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">ver&iacute;dica</strong>&nbsp;para que os resultados finais sejam dados de modo coeso com a finalidade da pesquisa.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"background: 0px 0px #ffffff; font-family: Raleway; font-size: 22px; margin: 40px 0px 20px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; top: 0px; left: 0px; cursor: text; font-weight: 500; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Tipos de gr&aacute;ficos</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Em estat&iacute;stica &eacute; muito comum a utiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o de diagramas para representar dados,&nbsp;<strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">diagramas</strong>&nbsp;<strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">s&atilde;o gr&aacute;ficos constru&iacute;dos em duas dimens&otilde;es</strong>, isto &eacute;, no plano. Existem v&aacute;rios modos de represent&aacute;-los, as principais s&atilde;o: gr&aacute;fico de pontos, gr&aacute;fico de linha, gr&aacute;fico de barra, gr&aacute;fico de coluna e gr&aacute;fico de setor.</p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Leia mais</strong>:&nbsp;<a style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" href=\"https://brasilescola.uol.com.br/matematica/moda-media-mediana.htm\">Moda, m&eacute;dia e mediana: n&uacute;meros que resumem informa&ccedil;&otilde;es de listas de dados</a></p>\r\n<ul style=\"background: 0px 0px #ffffff; font-family: Raleway; font-size: 20px; margin: 0px 0px 25px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; list-style-type: square !important;\">\r\n<li style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: initial !important; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px !important;\">\r\n<h3 style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 20px; margin: 40px 0px 20px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; position: initial; top: auto; left: auto; cursor: text; font-weight: 500; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Gr&aacute;fico de pontos</strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Tamb&eacute;m conhecido como&nbsp;<em style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Dotplot</em>, &eacute; utilizado quando possu&iacute;mos uma&nbsp;<a style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" href=\"https://brasilescola.uol.com.br/matematica/aplicacao-estatistica-frequencia-absoluta-frequencia-.htm\">tabela de distribui&ccedil;&atilde;o de frequ&ecirc;ncia</a>, sendo ela absoluta ou relativa. O gr&aacute;fico de pontos tem por objetivo apresentar os<strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;dados das tabelas de forma resumida</strong>&nbsp;e que possibilite a an&aacute;lise das distribui&ccedil;&otilde;es desses dados.</p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Exemplo</strong></p>\r\n<p>Suponha uma pesquisa, realizada em uma escola de educa&ccedil;&atilde;o infantil, na qual foram coletadas as idades das crian&ccedil;as. Nessa coleta foi organizado o seguinte rol:</p>\r\n<p>Rol: {1, 1, 2, 2, 2, 2, 3, 3, 4, 4, 4, 4, 4, 4, 5, 5, 6}</p>\r\n<p>Podemos organizar esses dados utilizando um&nbsp;<em style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Dotplot</em></p>\r\n<p><img style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://s1.static.brasilescola.uol.com.br/be/2020/03/grafico-pontos.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"455\" height=\"244\" /></p>\r\n<p>Observe que a quantidade de pontos corresponde &agrave; frequ&ecirc;ncia de cada idade e o somat&oacute;rio de todos os pontos fornece-nos a quantidade total de dados coletados.</p>\r\n<ul style=\"background: 0px 0px #ffffff; font-family: Raleway; font-size: 20px; margin: 0px 0px 25px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; list-style-type: square !important;\">\r\n<li style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: initial !important; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px !important;\">\r\n<h3 style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 20px; margin: 40px 0px 20px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; position: initial; top: auto; left: auto; cursor: text; font-weight: 500; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Gr&aacute;fico de linha</strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&Eacute; utilizado em casos que existe a necessidade de&nbsp;<strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">analisar dados ao longo do tempo</strong>, esse tipo de gr&aacute;fico &eacute; muito presente em an&aacute;lises financeiras. O eixo das abscissas (eixo x) representa o tempo, que pode ser dado em anos, meses, dias, horas etc., enquanto o eixo das ordenadas (eixo y) representa o outro dado em quest&atilde;o.</p>\r\n<p>Uma das vantagens desse tipo de gr&aacute;fico &eacute; a possibilidade de realizar a an&aacute;lise de mais de uma tabela, por exemplo.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"pub_insert_content_titulo\" style=\"background: 0px 0px #ffffff; font-family: Raleway; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">N&atilde;o pare agora... Tem mais depois da publicidade ;)</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"pub_insert_content\" style=\"background: 0px 0px #ffffff; font-family: Raleway; font-size: 20px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: auto; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 300px;\">\r\n<div style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 250px; width: 300px;\">\r\n<div id=\"banner-300x250-2-area\" style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px;\" data-google-query-id=\"CJiGtqrbk-oCFdYIuQYd7ggASQ\">\r\n<div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/8804/parceiros/brasil_escola_4__container__\" style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0pt none; display: inline-block; width: 300px; height: 250px;\"><iframe id=\"google_ads_iframe_/8804/parceiros/brasil_escola_4\" style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; vertical-align: bottom;\" title=\"3rd party ad content\" src=\"https://922d7aac15516ae67b287580c1bb729a.safeframe.googlesyndication.com/safeframe/1-0-37/html/container.html\" name=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"250\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" data-is-safeframe=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"5\" data-load-complete=\"true\"></iframe></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><strong style=\"background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; 